-- MOVES-RSA appoints William McDonnell as group chief risk officer
-- By Carolyn Cohn
-- Tue Oct 07, 2014 04:20AM EDT
-- None



LONDON, Oct 7 (Reuters) - Insurance company RSA <RSA.L> said on Tuesday it had appointed William McDonnell as group chief risk officer with effect from Dec. 1, 2014.

McDonnell will replace David Weymouth, who retires in May 2015, RSA said in a statement.